HEADWORD: Pas
<hw>Pas</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Pace</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A pace; a step, as in a
dance.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Right of going foremost; precedence.</def>
<rj><au>Arbuthnot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pasan</ent>⟦br⟧
